#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/custom_storage_helpers.py:335
msgctxt "GUI|Custom Partitioning|Confirm Delete Dialog"
msgid "Do _not show this dialog for other selected file systems."
msgstr "ບໍ່ຕ້ອງສະແດງກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບນີ້ສຳລັບລະບົບໄຟລ໌ອື່ນທີ່ເລືອກ (_n)."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/custom_storage_helpers.py:341
msgctxt "GUI|Custom Partitioning|Confirm Delete Dialog"
msgid "Delete _all file systems which are only used by {}."
msgstr "ລຶບທຸກລະບົບໄຟລ໌ທີ່ໃຊ້ໂດຍ {} ເທົ່ານັ້ນ (_a)."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/custom_storage_helpers.py:362
msgid ""
"{} may be a system boot partition! Deleting it may break other operating "
"systems. Are you sure you want to delete it?"
msgstr ""
"{} ອາດຈະເປັນພາຕິຊັນສຳລັບບູດລະບົບ! ການລຶບມັນອາດເຮັດໃຫ້ລະບົບປະຕິບັດການອື່ນເພພັງໄດ້. ທ່ານແນ່ໃຈບໍ່ວ່າຕ້ອ"
"ງການລຶບມັນ?"

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/custom_storage_helpers.py:368
msgid ""
"Are you sure you want to delete all of the data on {}, including subvolumes?"
msgstr "ທ່ານແນ່ໃຈບໍ່ວ່າຕ້ອງການລຶບຂໍ້ມູນທັງໝົດໃນ {}, ລວມເຖິງວໍລຸມຍ່ອຍນຳ?"

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/custom_storage_helpers.py:373
msgid ""
"Are you sure you want to delete all of the data on {}, including snapshots?"
msgstr "ທ່ານແນ່ໃຈບໍ່ວ່າຕ້ອງການລຶບຂໍ້ມູນທັງໝົດໃນ {}, ລວມເຖິງສະແນັບຊັອດນຳ?"

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/custom_storage_helpers.py:376
msgid "Are you sure you want to delete all of the data on {}?"
msgstr "ທ່ານແນ່ໃຈບໍ່ວ່າຕ້ອງການລຶບຂໍ້ມູນທັງໝົດໃນ {}?"

