#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/accordion.py:498
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You haven't created any mount points for your %(product)s %(version)s "
"installation yet.  You can:"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ສ້າງຈຸດເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ (mount point) ໃດໆສຳລັບການຕິດຕັ້ງ %(product)s %(version)s ຂອງທ່າ"
"ນເທື່ອ. ທ່ານສາມາດ:"

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/accordion.py:508
msgctxt "GUI|Custom Partitioning|Autopart Page"
msgid "_Click here to create them automatically."
msgstr "ຄລິກທີ່ນີ້ເພື່ອສ້າງແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດ (_C)."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/accordion.py:534
msgid "Create new mount points by clicking the '+' button."
msgstr "ສ້າງຈຸດເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ໃໝ່ໂດຍການຄລິກປຸ່ມ '+'."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/accordion.py:542
msgid ""
"Or, assign new mount points to existing partitions after selecting them "
"below."
msgstr ""
"ຫຼື, ກຳນົດຈຸດເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ໃໝ່ໃຫ້ກັບພາຕິຊັນທີ່ມີຢູ່ ຫຼັງຈາກທີ່ເລືອກພວກມັນຢູ່ດ້ານລຸ່ມ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/accordion.py:547
msgctxt "GUI|Custom Partitioning|Autopart Page"
msgid "_New mount points will use the following partitioning scheme:"
msgstr "ຈຸດເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ໃໝ່ຈະໃຊ້ຮູບແບບການແບ່ງພາຕິຊັນດັ່ງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ (_N):"

